➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：1.《在一只杯子里喊出海》
http://www.sohu.com/a/419508134_100115135	42373
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200919/a9a252e6ed1c496e8011efa3478fbca3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1.在一只杯子里喊出海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在一只杯子里喊出海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">海水苦涩咸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫过口岸津生波澜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满是生活的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蚂蚁越坎爬坡，在尘世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泅渡岁月苦海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>生存需要把日子煮沸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>波峰上希望开花，荡漾中前行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骨头里有雷声。不甘做绿苔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有种子喊出春天的海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喊出庄稼金色的浪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浪里有火风，烤香果实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总是怕醉意的粮仓囤积脂肪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泡开打皱的叶子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>褪去倦意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>时光的海在一只杯子里</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
